{{Infobox Union |name= CSA |country= [[Benin]] |affiliation= [[International Trade Union Confederation|ITUC]] |members= 20,000 |full_name= Autonomous Trade Unions Centre |native_name= Central des Syndicats Autonomes du Bénin |image= |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Cotonou]], Benin |people= [[Sanni Bonaventure]], president |website= |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Autonomous Trade Unions Centre''' is a [[trade union]] centre in [[Benin]]. It has a membership of 20,000 and is affiliated with the [[International Trade Union Confederation]]. It also works with the [[National Union of the Unions of the Workers of Benin]].
