'''''Bread and Milk''''' ([[Slovene language|Slovene]]: ''Kruh in mleko'') is a [[2001 in film|2001]] Slovene film [[Film director|directed]] by [[Jan Cvitkovič]]. It was Slovenia's submission to the [[74th Academy Awards]] for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film]], but was not accepted as a nominee.<ref name="51Submissions">{{cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2001/01.11.19.html |title=51 Countries In Race For Oscar |publisher=[[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] |date=2001-11-19 |accessdate=2008-08-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704083351/http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2001/01.11.19.html |archivedate=July 4, 2008 }}</ref><ref name="74thNomineesWinners">{{cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/74academyawards/nomswins.html|title=74th Academy Awards - Nominees and Winners|publisher=[[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]]|accessdate=2008-08-07 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080622045915/http://www.oscars.org/74academyawards/nomswins.html <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2008-06-22}}</ref>
