{{Politics of Andorra}}

'''Citizens' Initiative''' ({{lang-ca|Iniciativa Ciutadana}}, CI) is a political party in [[Andorra]] led by Sergi Ricart.

==History==
Established in 2012, the party ran in the [[Andorran parliamentary election, 2015|2015 parliamentary elections]] as part of a coalition with the [[Social Democratic Party of Andorra|Social Democratic Party]], the [[Greens of Andorra|Greens]] and independents. In the constituency elections the alliance received 24% of the vote but failed to win a seat. However, it also received 24% of the proportional representation vote, winning three seats.<ref>[http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2005_E.htm Last elections] IPU</ref>

