{{Infobox airport | name = Esperadinha Airport | image = Brava-94-123-12.jpg | caption = The airport in 1994 | IATA = BVR | ICAO = GVBR | type = Public | opened = 1992 | closed = 2004 | city-served = [[Brava, Cape Verde|Brava island]] | location = {{flag|Cape Verde}} | elevation-m = 20 | elevation-f = 64 | coordinates = {{coord|14|51|51.6|N|24|44|45.5|W|region:CV_type:airport|name=Esperadinha Airport (Esperadinha)|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Cape Verde | pushpin_mapsize = | pushpin_label = GVBR | pushpin_map_caption = Location of Esperadinha Airport in Cape Verde | r1-number = 05/23 | r1-length-m = 576 | r1-length-f = 1,890 | r1-surface = Asphalt | footnotes = Source: Landings.com<ref name="Landings">[http://aerobaticsweb.org/cgi-bin/search_apt?GVBR Airport record for Esperadinha Airport] at Landings.com. Retrieved 2013-08-25</ref><ref name="Google">{{Google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?ht=en&z=13&t=k&q=14.8643333333333,-24.7459722222222+%28Esperadinha+Airport%29|title=location of Esperadinha Airport|accessdate=2013-08-25}}</ref> }}
'''Esperadinha Airport''' {{Airport codes|BVR|GVBR}} was a public use [[airport]] located near the hamlet of [[Fajã de Água|Esperadinha]], northwestern [[Brava, Cape Verde|Brava]], [[Cape Verde]]. It opened in 1992 and operated until 2004, when it was closed due to persistent dangerous high winds. [[File:FajAeroporto.jpg|thumb|left|Former airport.]]
